metadata.name: BLOODBATH
metadata.description:
FTX Trading Ltd cryptocurrency exchange and the FTT token implodes in the Crypto markets 11/2022

Initial Reports and Sell-offs November 2nd-8th 2022
Withdrawals Freeze & Binance Deal collapses November 8th-11th 2022
Bankruptcy & Hacks November 11th 2022
Aftermath & Arrest November - Present
